      "side": 1,
      "message": "In the C library they\u0027re injected into the implementation by the compiler rather than through the public headers:\n\nhttps://github.com/openbmc/libpldm/blob/80cde632088394b9b3da90cf677b8d2763278c77/meson.build#L70\n\nIn light of the C++ support, maybe we should change that.",
